Marcial did many miracles and virtues. There was in that time a woman that had an husband sick of the palsy‚ to which woman S. Marcial delivered his bourdon‚ with which she touched a little her husband, and incontinent he was whole. Another time the fire was so great in the city of Bordeaux that all was on a flame. S. Marcial held up his bourdon against the fire and anon it was quenched.
